{"tid":355307,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"未經實戰 　美反導能力受質疑","createTime":"2017-08-11T07:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T15:11:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"40d20e97523b45b7b1182922d5a0baba1267a437","tid":355307,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:47:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20118160&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170811\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20118160%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170811&d=pFcolARE4D48kahgiC6wGUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=875df183\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20118160%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170811&h=71ab70fa\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20118160&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170811</a><br />\n<br />\n未經實戰 　美反導能力受質疑<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170811/large/11wf06p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170811%2Flarge%2F11wf06p.jpg&h=fb19c971&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「薩德」系統<br />\n<br />\n面對北韓導彈威脅，美國早前雖成功攔截模擬來自北韓的洲際彈道導彈，但測試被指在偏離實戰情況下進行，反導彈實力仍備受質疑。<br />\n美軍5月以「陸基中段防禦系統」（GMD）摧毀了一枚洲際導彈，但導彈防禦專家格雷戈（Laura Grego）認為該次測試未有全面考慮實際情況，如北韓會把導彈與看似是導彈的誘餌一同發射，以干擾美軍攔截器。<br />\n科學界普遍認為攔截導彈的難度猶如「以一枚子彈擊中另一枚」，因此美國自2010年五次測試GMD以來，僅兩次成功攔截目標。有專家更指出，成功例子從未在夜間發生，亦未知GMD能否應付一枚以上的導彈。換言之，北韓一旦在晚上發射導彈，或同時發射數枚導彈，GMD都未必能夠招架。<br />\n另有專家認為部署在關島的「戰區高空導彈防衞系統」（THAAD，又稱薩德）無能力同時攔截4枚導彈，建議美軍部署一至兩艘配備「神盾系統」的艦艇協助。<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n為免國際輕視　北韓勢成騎虎<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;10小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n特爆肚「烈焰與怒火」嚇窒幕僚<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;10小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n自揭作戰方案　平壤數萬人造勢北韓擬四彈齊發包圍關島<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;10小時前"},{"pid":"1a41a0ec0b7f03fa187211c0db8ddf872116d241","tid":355307,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人地SHOW比你睇,都係舊野啦"},{"pid":"a1f84d415b8bd7ee0255d9b0bf33adad3e5b3945","tid":355307,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:52:32.000Z","msg":"咁就真係要試試佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n北泡go go<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a546823540846562191db5a1ef93a2fb28711498","tid":355307,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有專家更指出，成功例子從未在夜間發生，亦未知GMD能否應付一枚以上的導彈。換言之，北韓一旦在晚上發射導彈，或同時發射數枚導彈，GMD都未必能夠招架。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 專家以為用對眼去追蹤導彈?"},{"pid":"ca69b53e3a3d186a9e7158d8912817e297386ba9","tid":355307,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T07:58:10.000Z","msg":"每支導彈都有一位空軍戴VR去控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb757964517c9933bde0bee627cc88ed83f534c1","tid":355307,"uid":113681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:01:32.000Z","msg":"篇文咁本係鱔稿畀金仔睇，等佢心雄開火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91be14e7d33010595c1732744e089e4ddb6e31a3","tid":355307,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"呢樣真<br />\n美國打得人多，俾人一打可能收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\